desktop-defaults (0.8.5) UNRELEASED; urgency=low

  * fll-kde-desktop.init: fix typo, s/korgacrc/korganizerrc/. Stop korganizer
    from starting up on live boot.
  * fll-kde-desktop.init: use more generic loop to populate
    ~/.kde/share/config.
  * Add desktop-defaults-gnome.install to keep live .gconf templates here
    instead of etcskel.
  * fll-gnome-desktop.init: use templates from desktop-defaults-gonme instead
    of relying on etcskel to have what we want.
  * fll-gnome-desktop.init: ensure we are preserving user ownership of
    dirs/files touched and created.
  * Really fix for korganizer. The file *is* named korgacrc but it defies the
    AutoStart standard in same way as kpowersave, it looks for Autostart
    (lower case "s"...).
  * Cleanup up ./kde.

 -- Kel Modderman <kel@otaku42.de>  Wed, 06 Jun 2007 15:51:15 +1000

